        <h4>What is Simulated Here?</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>The Fortress simulates a service that provides payroll and tax record keeping for small businesses. Such employers may lack the resources to store and secure critical data such as Social Security and bank account numbers.</li>
            <li>Although the data is not real, the security features on the site are similar to what such a business would actually use.</li>
            <li>Staff members serviced by The Fortress, and even business owners, have limited access to the data.  The security principle of least privilige means they can do what they need to do, and nothing more.</li>
